headline: Texas fines Booking.com $9.5m over hidden fees
summary: The settlement marks the largest US state action against an online travel agency for so-called “junk fees.”

headline: Fly High: Agoda Calls Out Asia's Key Birdwatching Destinations
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda is calling on all nature enthusiasts to flock to some of Asia's most enchanting birdwatching destinations. From seasoned birders to those new to the experience, travelers can enjoy a dual reward: the excitement of the spot and the chance to immerse themselves in spectacular landscapes.
